[style name="DefaultStyle"]
join Julia (JuliaDefault) right
Narrator: The phone awaits on the corner.
join Julia (JuliaSad0) right
Narrator: It's image, cold and dusty, both tempts and terrifies your bones.
join Julia (JuliaSad1) right
